{
  "texts": [
    "This architecture will be use in pre trained model for the object detection in computer vision [89] LeNet-5 CNN architecture is made up of 7 layers.",
    "The layer composition consists of 3 Convolutional layers, 2 subsampling layers and 2 fully connected layers.• The first layer is the input layer.",
    "In this layer you have a simple digit range from 0-9.",
    "It is a 32 × 32 grayscale image and each grayscale image have a digit range from 0-9.",
    "You need to classify what digit image has in it."
  ]
}